[[File:Harbour_256.png|right|256px]]
The '''Harbor''' is a building in [[Lord of Ultima]]. It allows for the transport of resources between cities and enables you to trade with other players by sea. Also increases the tax income of connected [[Townhouse]]s.

'''Requirements:''' [[Town Hall]] Level 10

